These two files are contributed by Chris DeVisser, our 2016 winter term SE350 (Operating Systems) student. The code piece is inspired by the article at: https://gustedt.wordpress.com/2010/08/14/scope-bound-resource-management-with-for-scopes/

Your will need to enable armcc --c99 (Target Option -> C/C++ -> Misc Control textfield: enter --c99 in Keil uVision IDE).
